Ikechukwu Onunaku, onye a maara dịka Ikechukwu na Killz bụ onye Naijiria na-agụ egwu, onye na-eti egwu, na onye na-eme ihe nkiri onyonyo
Ọ bụ onye otu na The Wedding Party na The Wedding Party 2: Destination Dubai
A mụrụ Onunaku na Manassas, Virginia na nne na nna Naijiria mana a zụlitere ya na Lagos, Nigeria
Ọ kwagara United States mgbe ọ gụsịrị ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị na King's College, Lagos
Ọ laghachiri ihe karịrị afọ iri ka e mesịrị na Naịjirịa obere oge tupu ewepụta abọm mbụ ya bụ Son of the Soil n'afọ 2006 nke gosipụtara egwu My Name is Ikechukwu
Nwa nke Ala sochiri Life and Times of Killz Volume 1 nke gosipụtara mmepụta nke Don Jazzy na mpụta nke DBanj na Wande Coal na onye na-arụkọ ọrụ ugboro ugboro Naeto C.
Egwu ya "My name is Ikechukwu" nke sitere na Son of the Soil nke edepụtara na No.1 na East, na Lagos na Abuja maka izu 21, isii na ise n'otu n'otu
Abọm nke atọ ya bụ The Alliance Reconstructed gosipụtara egwu ndị ọzọ dịka "Critical", na "Now is the Time"
Egwu ya ndị ọzọ gụnyere "Bu Lie Oto, B.A.D.A, Carry Me, Balabala..""
O mere nke mbụ ya na nnukwu ihuenyo na obere ihe nkiri nke Walter Taylaur's The Wages mepụtara ma duzie
Ọ gara n'ihu nweta otuto dị egwu, ahọpụtara maka nyocha na AFRIFF 2014 ma mesịa merie obere ihe kachasị mma na AMVCA'S na 2015
N'ịgbaso nke ahụ site na nnukwu mpụta na Gidi Up nke Ndani mepụtara, Ikechukwu nwetara nnukwu ọrụ na nnukwu ihe nkiri The Wedding Party na 2016
N'afọ 2017, ọ laghachiri n'ihe nkiri nke The Wedding Party 2
N'afọ 2019, Ikechukwu wepụtara egwu ọzọ, Nnukwu Azu

N'ọnwa Septemba afọ 2019, Ikechukwu dere ihe na ibe Instagram ya, na-ekwu na a kpọpụtara ya n'ime tagzi Uber, tinye ya n'ime ụgbọala ndị uwe ojii ma tie ya ihe site n'aka ndị ọrụ ndị uwe ojii Naịjirịa
O kwuru na a kpọgara ya na ATM ma manye ya ka ọ wụfuo akaụntụ ụlọ akụ ya.
Ọ lụrụ onye nlereanya Britain bụ Ella na Mee 2021, onye sitere na Imo steeti na nwa nwanyị nke onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị Naịjirịa.
